1930;;Part Time Wife;;American;;Leo McCarey;;Edmund Lowe, Leila Hyams;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Part_Time_Wife;;Jim Murdock's marriage is in trouble after he neglects his wife, particularly her attraction to golf. With tips from Irish caddy Tommy Milligan on how to play the game on the course and at home, Jim challenges his estranged wife to a match and demonstrates that he's a changed man.